1. *Ruci* su mu se trgle od umora. (His hands started trembling from exhaustion.)
2. Ona nije znala gde da *ruče*. (She didn't know where to sit.)
3. On je stavio svoje *ruke* na ramena deteta. (He put his hands on the child's shoulders.)
4. Ona je stavila svoje *ruke* oko vrata deteta. (She put her arms around the child's neck.)
5. Ona je primila svoju *ručnu* torbu. (She took her handbag.)
6. Ona se trgla i povukla *ruke*. (She jerked and pulled away her hands.)